guide: Obtain all possible elements using only Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Explorers of Sky.
-A good setup for recruiting is a leader with Fast Friend (ex: Chikorita) and a Pokémon with Illuminate ability (ex: Lanturn).
-A good Pokémon for clearing Zero Isle South is Smoochum.
-Fastest way to level up or raise IQ Pokémon is with a leader with Nature Gifter (ex: Chikorita) and eat Joy Seed, Golden Seed, and Gummmies.
-Check Recruitment Guide and Speedrun Guide to get all Pokémon efficiently.
Play Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Explorers of Sky on another savefile.
-Faint in a dungeon and send an SOS mail to your main Pokémon Sky, enter the SOS mail password and rescue the player.
-Connect the two games wirelessly to transfer a team to the main Pokémon Sky to unlock Explorer Maze.
